Text.SourceString: Hey there, traveler, looking for decor?//Oh, hang on, you’re from around here, aren't you? '<PlayerName>$Player</>' is it?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, traveler, looking for decor?//Oh, hang on, you’re from around here, aren't you? '<PlayerName>$Player</>' is it?

Text.SourceString: Hmm...yeah?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm...yeah?

Text.SourceString: Hey there, looking for decor?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, looking for decor?

Text.SourceString: Greetings, my artistic friend! Has the tide brought you to seek beauty?//You've come to the right place!
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, my artistic friend! Has the tide brought you to seek beauty?//You've come to the right place!

Text.SourceString: Ah, a connoisseur's eye I see! Welcome!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, a connoisseur's eye I see! Welcome!

Text.SourceString: Hello there! In search of something to transform your grotto?//Galoong's creations promise nothing less than magic.
Text.LocalizedString: Hello there! In search of something to transform your grotto?//Galoong's creations promise nothing less than magic.

Text.SourceString: Welcome, welcome! Take a look at my collection, won’t you?//Who knows, perhaps one of these wonders is just waiting to go home with you
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome, welcome! Take a look at my collection, won’t you?//Who knows, perhaps one of these wonders is just waiting to go home with you

Text.SourceString: Welcome to my shop! How may I assist you today?
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome to my shop! How may I assist you today?

Text.SourceString: Greetings, and welcome! How are you doing today, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings, and welcome! How are you doing today, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: Have you come here to chat or to shop?
Text.LocalizedString: Have you come here to chat or to shop?

Text.SourceString: I once told Lanin if she kept selling those plain tunics, I'd start sculpting in monochrome just to give her a taste of bland!//Oh, that sounded a bit harsh, didn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: I once told Lanin if she kept selling those plain tunics, I'd start sculpting in monochrome just to give her a taste of bland!//Oh, that sounded a bit harsh, didn't it?

Text.SourceString: Lanin's shop is simply delightful; I've even picked up a top here myself.
Text.LocalizedString: Lanin's shop is simply delightful; I've even picked up a top here myself.

Text.SourceString: Lanin and I go way back—she was my darling long before Galoong came into the picture.//Oh, but not romantically, darling. Read the room...she’s my best friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Lanin and I go way back—she was my darling long before Galoong came into the picture.//Oh, but not romantically, darling. Read the room...she’s my best friend.

Text.SourceString: I spend so much time here with Lanin, we might as well be married, ha ha!//Just kidding. I LOVE YOU DEARLY, LANIN. BUT NOT IN THAT WAY.
Text.LocalizedString: I spend so much time here with Lanin, we might as well be married, ha ha!//Just kidding. I LOVE YOU DEARLY, LANIN. BUT NOT IN THAT WAY.

Text.SourceString: Being here in the shop is never dull.//I actually look forward to it...spending time with my dear friend is always a highlight.
Text.LocalizedString: Being here in the shop is never dull.//I actually look forward to it...spending time with my dear friend is always a highlight.

Text.SourceString: Lanin inspired one of my most beloved pieces, you know.//She mentioned loving the iridescence of mussel shells, so I crafted a series of shimmering mussel-shell mosaics.
Text.LocalizedString: Lanin inspired one of my most beloved pieces, you know.//She mentioned loving the iridescence of mussel shells, so I crafted a series of shimmering mussel-shell mosaics.

Text.SourceString: They glint just like her vibrant personality!
Text.LocalizedString: They glint just like her vibrant personality!

Text.SourceString: We once threw a fashion and art soirée right here between our stalls.//Lanin dressed everyone in silks, and I provided sculptures as backdrops.//'A night of style and stone,' we called it—truly a splash hit!
Text.LocalizedString: We once threw a fashion and art soirée right here between our stalls.//Lanin dressed everyone in silks, and I provided sculptures as backdrops.//'A night of style and stone,' we called it—truly a splash hit!

Text.SourceString: Galoong and I, we have this ongoing jest—whose craft draws more eyes.//I draped his corner in seaweed garlands overnight; he woke to what he called 'the fanciest forest.'//Oh, how we laughed with the morning tide!
Text.LocalizedString: Galoong and I, we have this ongoing jest—whose craft draws more eyes.//I draped his corner in seaweed garlands overnight; he woke to what he called 'the fanciest forest.'//Oh, how we laughed with the morning tide!

Text.SourceString: I dream of crafting a sculpture so vast, it spans the breadth of the Mermaid’s Trench.//Imagine, a piece that can be seen, like a beacon, from any corner of the ocean.
Text.LocalizedString: I dream of crafting a sculpture so vast, it spans the breadth of the Mermaid’s Trench.//Imagine, a piece that can be seen, like a beacon, from any corner of the ocean.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the dreaded artist’s block. I feel for Galoong; he's been having a hard time creating lately.//I wish there were something I could do to help him...
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the dreaded artist’s block. I feel for Galoong; he's been having a hard time creating lately.//I wish there were something I could do to help him...

Text.SourceString: I think it's the cold water. It seems to block creativity, doesn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: I think it's the cold water. It seems to block creativity, doesn't it?

Text.SourceString: Caring for sculptures, my love, is like tending to a garden of jewels.//A gentle polish with saltwater, and they'll gleam like new!
Text.LocalizedString: Caring for sculptures, my love, is like tending to a garden of jewels.//A gentle polish with saltwater, and they'll gleam like new!

Text.SourceString: My hand is tired...sculpting isn't kind to the hands.
Text.LocalizedString: My hand is tired...sculpting isn't kind to the hands.

Text.SourceString: Oh, when Galoong gets going on a new piece, you can forget about meals.//Honestly, I'm the same way—there's something about being absorbed into art that just eats time!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, when Galoong gets going on a new piece, you can forget about meals.//Honestly, I'm the same way—there's something about being absorbed into art that just eats time!

Text.SourceString: I wonder if Todi has restocked my favorite labus yet.//I've been craving it lately—can almost taste it on the tip of my tongue.
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder if Todi has restocked my favorite labus yet.//I've been craving it lately—can almost taste it on the tip of my tongue.

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking about starting a small garden, something modest.//But it does seem a bit inconvenient, doesn't it? What do you think—should I dive into it?
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking about starting a small garden, something modest.//But it does seem a bit inconvenient, doesn't it? What do you think—should I dive into it?

Text.SourceString: I woke up bursting with ideas today!//I’m thinking of a sculpture series inspired by the phases of the moon—each one a different mood of the ocean.
Text.LocalizedString: I woke up bursting with ideas today!//I’m thinking of a sculpture series inspired by the phases of the moon—each one a different mood of the ocean.

Text.SourceString: I’ve started using seaweed wraps on my hands at night—wonders for the aches!//Keeps the fingers nimble and the joints soft.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve started using seaweed wraps on my hands at night—wonders for the aches!//Keeps the fingers nimble and the joints soft.

Text.SourceString: Swimming around, are we?
Text.LocalizedString: Swimming around, are we?

Text.SourceString: You look like you're having a splendid day.//It's good to see.
Text.LocalizedString: You look like you're having a splendid day.//It's good to see.

Text.SourceString: You look positively buoyant today! Whatever's in the water, I'll have a sip too.
Text.LocalizedString: You look positively buoyant today! Whatever's in the water, I'll have a sip too.

Text.SourceString: Seeing you this chipper is nice! What's the secret, my friend?
Text.LocalizedString: Seeing you this chipper is nice! What's the secret, my friend?

Text.SourceString: You're beaming brighter than a bioluminescent bloom tonight!
Text.LocalizedString: You're beaming brighter than a bioluminescent bloom tonight!

Text.SourceString: Ah, such a radiant smile! Having a good day, my friend?
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, such a radiant smile! Having a good day, my friend?

Text.SourceString: I start each morning with a swim through the coral gardens—it clears my mind and readies my head for the day.
Text.LocalizedString: I start each morning with a swim through the coral gardens—it clears my mind and readies my head for the day.

Text.SourceString: Negotiating with the pearl divers is always a dance, and frankly, I hate it.//It should be simple—name your price and let's skip the games. I'm here for pearls, not theatrics.
Text.LocalizedString: Negotiating with the pearl divers is always a dance, and frankly, I hate it.//It should be simple—name your price and let's skip the games. I'm here for pearls, not theatrics.

Text.SourceString: One of my goals is to sculpt a piece so large it can be seen from above the surface—a true landmark of the deep.
Text.LocalizedString: One of my goals is to sculpt a piece so large it can be seen from above the surface—a true landmark of the deep.

Text.SourceString: I'd probably make more money traveling and selling, but honestly, one of the things I look forward to the most is going home to Galoong.//I don't think I'd last too long without him.
Text.LocalizedString: I'd probably make more money traveling and selling, but honestly, one of the things I look forward to the most is going home to Galoong.//I don't think I'd last too long without him.

Text.SourceString: My favorite stone to carve comes from the North Sea, and my second favorite is actually from a cavern on land.//A land-dweller sold them to me.
Text.LocalizedString: My favorite stone to carve comes from the North Sea, and my second favorite is actually from a cavern on land.//A land-dweller sold them to me.

Text.SourceString: The princess is very skilled at sculpting. I trained her myself.//She doesn't spend much time around the kingdom, though. I think she prefers to explore beyond its borders.
Text.LocalizedString: The princess is very skilled at sculpting. I trained her myself.//She doesn't spend much time around the kingdom, though. I think she prefers to explore beyond its borders.

Text.SourceString: The seaweed in this part of the sea isn't the best, I hate to say.//It'll do fine, just isn't top quality.
Text.LocalizedString: The seaweed in this part of the sea isn't the best, I hate to say.//It'll do fine, just isn't top quality.

Text.SourceString: I accidentally lay on a mini crab—it was playing on my seabed. Luckily, it didn't get hurt.//Why are there so many crabs around here?
Text.LocalizedString: I accidentally lay on a mini crab—it was playing on my seabed. Luckily, it didn't get hurt.//Why are there so many crabs around here?

Text.SourceString: I once ended up floating on my roof! There was a massive storm, and I forgot to secure my blanket.//You be careful out there!
Text.LocalizedString: I once ended up floating on my roof! There was a massive storm, and I forgot to secure my blanket.//You be careful out there!

Text.SourceString: While I was plucking my chin hair today, it suddenly came to me—ah, I think I'll cook some kebabs tonight.//Doesn't that sound delicious? Kebabs, yum!
Text.LocalizedString: While I was plucking my chin hair today, it suddenly came to me—ah, I think I'll cook some kebabs tonight.//Doesn't that sound delicious? Kebabs, yum!

Text.SourceString: Avoid meddling with the creatures of the Deep Sea.//They're aggressive for a reason—best to leave them undisturbed.
Text.LocalizedString: Avoid meddling with the creatures of the Deep Sea.//They're aggressive for a reason—best to leave them undisturbed.

Text.SourceString: It's a bit disheartening to settle for second-quality seaweed, but honestly, even our second best is still top-notch in here.
Text.LocalizedString: It's a bit disheartening to settle for second-quality seaweed, but honestly, even our second best is still top-notch in here.

Text.SourceString: The surface world doesn't intrigue me.//There's a reason I have a fin and a tail instead of legs—I'm not designed to just swim up and walk. Sometimes, we need to respect nature's design.
Text.LocalizedString: The surface world doesn't intrigue me.//There's a reason I have a fin and a tail instead of legs—I'm not designed to just swim up and walk. Sometimes, we need to respect nature's design.

Text.SourceString: I heard the sand on the surface can be scorching hot, so hot that people apply some sort of stew to prevent burning.//That sounds quite intimidating to me!
Text.LocalizedString: I heard the sand on the surface can be scorching hot, so hot that people apply some sort of stew to prevent burning.//That sounds quite intimidating to me!

Text.SourceString: I encourage everyone to try sculpting at least once.//And if you’re proud of your creation, why not sell it through my shop? We can work out a fair fee.
Text.LocalizedString: I encourage everyone to try sculpting at least once.//And if you’re proud of your creation, why not sell it through my shop? We can work out a fair fee.
